{"tid":2146442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔理咩原因都好，外國人真係好幫香港人，又收留我地又幫我地幫仇，古今中外都好少可幫到咁盡，我地要好好記住同感恩","createTime":"2020-08-08T14:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T16:46:11.000Z","uid":31215,"like":97,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"044fcf8fe462f2567fa94c937ca79cc06baedc3e","tid":2146442,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"由政府，朝野，到普通市民<br />\n對香港人都係好同情同支持，而且願意提供幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未睇過呢條片可以睇吓普通人點睇香港情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sDgNsNCFAMA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsDgNsNCFAMA&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiWxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=009d3d94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sDgNsNCFAMA</a><br />\n有人話咩為選票，咩政治考慮<br />\n我唔否定<br />\n但客觀效果真係幫左我地好多<br />\n而且唔淨係美國，包括好多其他國家，就算政府唔支持啲人民都支持我地<br />\n<br />\n滴水之恩，湧泉相報<br />\n我地呢個世代要記住呢份恩情<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n移民撚就做好自己唔好影衰香港人<br />\n我地日後有能力同有機會都要幫返人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5c75be96ca37b8e5dfca75147a599f33a96854","tid":2146442,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:45:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1dedc0e420850bd0d7e2e13c1b1c33d559f95c94","tid":2146442,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:46:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"77ad4a90f4e6279c0c6cd38a96c3d854c8ece604","tid":2146442,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:46:39.000Z","msg"